      <title>戴蒙批评巴塞尔协议III残局，称其“有害”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-06/dimon-criticizes-basel-iii-endgame-calls-it-harmful-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通董事长兼首席执行官杰米戴蒙就美国政府拟议的银行监管计划作证。戴蒙在参议院银行委员会作证时表示，拟议的任何改变都无法阻止硅谷银行的倒闭。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-06/dimon-criticizes-basel-iii-endgame-calls-it-harmful-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 15:25:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
